HEADWORD: Vacuate
<hw>Vac"u*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>vacuatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>vacuare</ets> to empty, from
<ets>vacuus</ets> empty. See <er>Vacant</er>.]</ety> <def>To make void,
